      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWEET BEVELY ANN (5) shapes well for this backing up a convincing 19.42 win with success at this track over 340m last time, recording 19.61. Expected to push the clock again here. LEVINGS (1) scored two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 8 length 4th at this track (20.03). The form from his last run stacks up well. Should play a prominent role. BLUE SUPREME (2) finds it hard to break through. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing third (19.93) at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Well-placed to take this out. HAYMAN BEACH (4) returns after a break and looks a top-three hope.",
